{"tid":326079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳沃爾瑪斬人案2死9傷　家人指疑犯有精神病","createTime":"2017-07-17T16:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T16:56:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab48f9fdbc5cb1cc409e0bcb622163596855c40","tid":326079,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:42:18.000Z","msg":"2017年7月17日 星期一<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170717/s00004/19cc7c8b99057020b69d84ade86561f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170717%2Fs00004%2F19cc7c8b99057020b69d84ade86561f8.jpg&h=803686bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深圳一間沃爾瑪超級市場昨晚(16日)發生亂刀斬人縱火案，造成2死9傷，公安事後拘捕一名重慶姓蔣男子。<br />\n《京華時報》報導，該名姓蔣疑犯的家人昨晚接到深圳警方的通知，得悉蔣在深圳殺了人。疑犯的父親透露，蔣有精神病，他自3至4年前離家打工後就沒有見過兒子。<br />\n蔣的外甥亦向記者表示，蔣犯病時會打人，不犯病時則比較少說話，又稱家人都曾被其打過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170717/s00004/1500268648954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170717%2Fs00004%2F1500268648954&d=ufi%2FbvJ5JefyUmEdKwOPsx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=88d68c4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170717%2Fs00004%2F1500268648954&h=1d680448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170717/s00004/1500268648954</a>"},{"pid":"0d0b6350656c887a17242a4ae4fad58aef91b33a","tid":326079,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"見怪不怪 支那入面都習慣曬"},{"pid":"97bedd9cb423e254b0fb47144f6e6a474ea3549b","tid":326079,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:53:34.000Z","msg":"死得咁少..."},{"pid":"6f2eb9c91fae47e4e66bc4d67054d21aceff30ea","tid":326079,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"日日150個遲早輪到香港<img src=\"/asset